  "keyFeatures": [
    "Virtual filesystem mounting (FUSE) and .strm file generation",
    "Automatic media organization using TorBox Metadata Search API",
    "Support for Jellyfin, Emby, Plex, and other media players",
    "Cross-platform compatibility (Linux, macOS, Windows via .strm)",
    "Docker and local Python installation support",
    "Automatic library updates and refresh scheduling",
    "Raw mode for preserving original file structure"
